===Awards===

* ACBL Player of the Year (1) 1998
* [[Fishbein Trophy]] (1) 1998
* [[Herman Trophy]] (1) 1976
* [[Mott-Smith Trophy]] (1) 2002

===Wins===

* [[Bermuda Bowl]] (5) 1976, 1977, 1979, 2000, 2003 <ref>[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[Cavendish Invitational|Cavendish Invitational Pairs]] (1) 1995 <ref>[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[Buffett Cup]] (1) 2006 

